Muffin-Admin
#############

.. _description:

Muffin-Admin -- an extension to Muffin_ that implements admin-interfaces

.. _badges:

.. image:: http://img.shields.io/travis/klen/muffin-admin.svg?style=flat-square
    :target: http://travis-ci.org/klen/muffin-admin
